Package: pasystray
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgtk-3-0, libpulse0, libavahi-client3, libavahi-glib1, libnotify4, gnome-icon-theme-full, libappindicator3-1
Description: PulseAudio system tray - a padevchooser replacement
 PaSystray provides a system tray icon to control the PulseAudio daemon. It
 supports changing the default source/sink, detecting remote source/sinks and
 moving streams to other souce/sinks on the fly.
